Introduction


RUBY (Korean: 루비) was a South Korean girl group that debuted in 2012 under the label HY Entertainment. They started as a dance group in 2011 but made their debut on April 9, 2012 with the digital single, “Get Down“. They disbanded sometime in 2013.
